asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Nebula
description:
This chick loves her mycelium! She’s nibbled on so much of it that she blasted off on a mind expanding journey through space and time, into the heart of a supernova, through its black hole and into a new state of being with just a stardust cloud of her former self remaining. . . this is where she earned her name, Nebula.
 
Although she may look like she’s away with the fairies, she actually sees all. Neb’s cosmic trip has given her a depth of insight and perspective far beyond that of other mere mortal bunnies, so she hops through life without ego, without judgement of herself or others. Her ego dissolved into dust the moment her mind’s eye passed through the supernova, bringing her total inner peace. So now she just grooves through life, nibbling on her mycelium, because she knows that everything is exactly as it’s supposed to be.
 
Namaste fluffy, my friends.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Fooking Legend
description: Formerly known as FOO, this was the Fluf that started it all. However, FOO was mercilessly framed for murder in a vile plot to assassinate Scroge McFluf gone wrong. Lucky for Scroge, his first in command who was known for his gluttonous ways ate the poisoned carrot that was destined for him. A classic case of stolen identity the facts were pointed at FOO by his evil and sinister namesake Foo. After serving 14 months (11.6 yrs in humanoid timeframes) behind bars with no carrots, just weed infested prison grass, FOO is out for revenge and will undoubtedly prevail. A dish best served cold, he is planning to jump Foo when he least expects it. The lore of the Flufs will be upheld and a Fooking Legend will be born! To be continued...

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

description: Ever since he was born, in fact, destined before even being conceived, this FLUF was a keeper of time, a master of maximising every drop of the special element that most dont value as the most precious resource. You can also catch him experiencing time in other dimensions when he eats lots of his favourite thing, mushrooms.
